uproot4.source.xrootd.XRootDVectorReadSource(\r\n    \"root://eospublic.cern.ch//eos/opendata/lhcb/AntimatterMatters2017/data/B2HHH_MagnetDown.root\",\r\n    max_num_elements=5\r\n), basic_ranges)\r\n```\r\n\r\nRelated to #2.", "created_at": "2020-05-15T17:52:03Z", "updated_at": "2020-05-16T08:25:04Z", "closed_at": "2020-05-15T21:50:44Z", "merged_at": "2020-05-15T21:50:44Z", "merge_commit_sha": "300a02b37c4a7121f6d5aa70ceb3920a52b48eb4", "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/uproot5/pulls/4/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/uproot5/pulls/4/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/uproot5/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/uproot5/issues/4/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/uproot5/statuses/f292df31bc0b8155dcbe03177470f2b8acf44512", "head": {"label": "chrisburr:xrootd-vector-read", "ref": "xrootd-vector-read", "sha": "f292df31bc0b8155dcbe03177470f2b8acf44512", "user": {"login": "chrisburr", "id": 5220533, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjUyMjA1MzM=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5220533?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr", "html_url": "https://github.com/chrisburr", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chrisburr/events{/privacy}